.Xr isupper 3 ,
.Xr isxdigit 3 ,
.Xr stdio 3 ,
.Xr tolower 3 ,
.Xr toupper 3 ,
.Xr ascii 7
.Sh STANDARDS
The
.Fn toascii
function conforms to
.St -xpg4
and
.St -p1003.1-2001 .
The
.St -p1003.1-2008
revision however marked it as obsolete, noting that
.Fn toascii
cannot be used portably in a localized application.
